            <title>[FLINK-20063] File Source requests an additional split on every restore.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-20063</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently, the &lt;tt&gt;FileSourceReader&lt;/tt&gt; requests a new split when started. That includes cases when it was restored from a checkpoint.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So with every restore, the reader increases its split backlog size by one, causing problems for balanced split assignments.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
